content_html:
Visit Scheduled for Thursday Afternoon

Speaker of Parliament, Devraj Ghimire, will visit the Parliament building that was set on fire during the Jana Andolan (People's Movement). His secretariat has announced that the visit is scheduled for Thursday at 12 PM
